decision_conditions:
&lt;p&gt;Repointing shall be carried out using a lime-based mortar consisting of 1 part lime to 3 parts sand. Cementitious mortars
shall not be used. Pointing shall be in a slightly (2/3mm) recessed style and not flush, bucket handle, ribbon, weather struck, or raised pointing.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to preserving or enhancing the character and appearance of the conservation area.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
